title: Things You Can’t Beat🎙#195
description:
The gang has returned from their hunting trip (02:19) where the Mossberg’s couldn’t have shot any straighter, and the birds couldn’t have been more dead to rights. Myles also put on a drinking clinic over the weekend and he did not disappoint, the hotel they stayed at did though. (17:25) Later on Ryan introduces his very first segment, “Things that can’t be beat” (42:53) and Tyler tries bringing up something that can’t be beat, however, it turns out it can, actually, a lot of things can beat it. (57:41)
